{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/clearnotificationcenter"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/clearNotificationCenter","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)clearNotificationCenter","title":"clearNotificationCenter","symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Type Method","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"clearNotificationCenter"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"clearNotificationCenter"}]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Clears all delivered notifications from the notification center."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"clearNotificationCenter","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Removes all notifications delivered by your app from the iOS Notification Center.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"This is commonly used when:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"User opens the app (clear notifications since they’re viewing content)"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"User logs out (clear notifications for privacy)"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Content is marked as read in-app"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Performing a “mark all as read” action"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Only removes notifications from your app; other apps’ notifications are unaffected."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Example","type":"heading","anchor":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Clear notifications on app activation and logout:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class NotificationManager {","","    func applicationDidBecomeActive() {","        \/\/ Clear notifications when user opens app","        Pushwoosh.configure.clearNotificationCenter()","","        \/\/ Also reset badge","        UIApplication.shared.applicationIconBadgeNumber = 0","        Pushwoosh.configure.sendBadges(0)","    }","","    func handleUserLogout() {","        \/\/ Clear notifications for privacy","        Pushwoosh.configure.clearNotificationCenter()","","        \/\/ Unregister from push","        Pushwoosh.configure.unregisterForPushNotifications { _ in }","","        \/\/ Clear user identity","        Pushwoosh.configure.setUserId(\"\")","    }","","    func markAllAsRead() {","        \/\/ Clear from notification center","        Pushwoosh.configure.clearNotificationCenter()","","        \/\/ Update backend","        APIClient.shared.markAllNotificationsRead { _ in }","","        \/\/ Clear badge","        Pushwoosh.configure.sendBadges(0)","    }","}"]}]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/clearNotificationCenter":{"kind":"symbol","title":"clearNotificationCenter","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/clearNotificationCenter","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Clears all delivered notifications from the notification center."}],"ur